"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.1.6\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.1.6</span> 標題：鐮刀（sickle）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： חֶרְמֵשׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： chermesh)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:9\">DEU 16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:26\">DEU 23:26</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מַגָּל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： magal)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:16\">JER 50:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel4:13\">JOL 4:13</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： δρέπανον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： drepanon)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:29\">MRK 4:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:14\">REV 14:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:15\">REV 14:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:16\">REV 14:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:17\">REV 14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:18\">REV 14:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:18\">REV 14:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:19\">REV 14:19</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0320_cutting_grain_sickle.jpg\" alt=\"男子用鐮刀割穀物\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">男子用鐮刀割穀物 (The Pictorial New Testament, The Religious Tract Society 1881, Public domain)</figcaption></figure>鐮刀是一種比較大的弧形刀具，裝有一個較短的木柄（15—20厘米或6—8英吋），用來割下成熟了的穀物。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0321_sickle.jpg\" alt=\"鐮刀\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">鐮刀 (© Juan R. Lascorz, CC BY-SA 3.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>使用者將鐮刀貼近地面、以圓弧動作揮舞，將草或麥子割下。使用短柄鐮刀貼近地面工作時，人需要彎下腰來；如果使用長柄鐮刀，則可以站著工作（另參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">2.15.1 車輪彎刀（戰車武器）（scythe [chariot weapon]）&lt;REALIA:2.15.1&gt;</a> ）。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>如果目標語言中沒有「鐮刀」一詞，翻譯者可使用描述性的短語，如「用來割麥子的彎刀」、「收割鈎」，或「收割用的大砍刀」。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:0\">REV 14:0</a> ，鐮刀出現在若干慣用語中，這可能會讓讀者感到困惑。例如，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:15\">REV 14:15</a> 不應按照原文字面譯成「伸進去你的鐮刀，收割吧」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 採用直譯），而是應該譯成「用你的鐮刀收割莊稼吧」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 英文直譯），這樣會更清楚。古代以色列人不使用長柄鐮刀。如果翻譯者必須在短柄鐮刀和長柄鐮刀之間做出選擇，則前者更為準確。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
